kiosk-minimal
===================

Puppet module to install a simple kiosk browser.It installs bare Xorg, Openbox window manager and:

kiosk-minimal::video = MPV package and auto starting local video
kiosk-minimal::web = Chrome browser gpu forced with transparent mouse cursor

Parameters
-------------
All parameters are read from defaults in init.pp and can be overwritten by The foreman.

```
kiosk-minimal::video >
$packages                             = ['xorg','openbox','openjdk-7-jre','p7zip-full','build-essential'],

kiosk-minimal::web >
$packages                             = ['xorg','openbox','openjdk-7-jre','p7zip-full','build-essential'],
```
Limitations
-------------
This module has been built on and tested against Puppet 4.

The module has been tested on
- Ubuntu Server 16.04.

Dependencies
-------------
- stdlib

